channel.title: [RS2] - Freddy1990's Featherbuyer V5.10
channel.description:
Once again, a new version of my featherbuyer, one of my trademarks :p Nothing special, just designed to do the job. The structure and coding quality of the scipt may differ in some places, but thats because it's is still based on my first version which was 100% coordinate based back at kaitnieks when i first started. I made it read the number of feathers this time so that it'll still buy them if there are more than 1000 in the shop.
[code]<----- Freddy1990's FeatherBuyer V5.10 -----> The script has been running for 00:01:38. The script has bought feathers 10 times. The script has bought 100 feathers. You have 509000 coins left. <------------------------------------------->[/code]
Enjoy;)

item.title: [RS2] - Freddy1990's Featherbuyer V5.10
item.dc:creator: @drahlee drahlee
item.description:
@drahlee wrote:

This is how it works…theres a 1000 feathers…it buys 10 and once the feathers go back up to 1000 it buys again and so on. you cant set a limit just do some math and put how much money you want on the account and itll buy till its out of money. It wont work for more then 6 hours or it wont work if thers more 100k in your inveetory otherwise it kicks ass also when your out of cash it logs out. something i was worrying about. works great for me! i hope that answers your questions. it would be nice if someone can solve the 100k thing but its not a biggie. good script besides the fact its the only feather buyer script i can find lol
